3.  Again, this is exactly why I would prefer the Flame Lick line upgrade.  If our spell lines were all just fleshed out fully, I think a lot of druids would be happier without new types of spells.  Right now, while we are supposed to be versatile, we are just limited to a couple of spell lines which are close to being developed -- Wings of Death, NT/CB, Wildfire (in conjunction with Sundering).<br>
<br>
