<br>
Fire DoT line -- should continue as shown in my first post.<br>
<br>
Glamour of Tunare -- would be nice to get one that it to Glamour that Tashanian is to Tashani.<br>
<br>
Share Wolf Form -- a form of this that adds atk, similar to Form of the Great Wolf, or even one that adds mana like Form of the Howler.<br>
<br>
Wake of Karana -- one that stops snow.<br>
<br>
Summon Drink and Food -- Abundant Drink and Food<br>
